288.4	Steve_Ballmer	Steve Ballmer	Steven Anthony "Steve" Ballmer (born March 24, 1956) is the chief executive officer of Microsoft, having held that post since January 2000. As of 2012 , his personal wealth is estimated at US$15.7 billion, ranking number 19 on the Forbes 400.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Steve_Ballmer_at_CES_2010_cropped.jpg/220px-Steve_Ballmer_at_CES_2010_cropped.jpg
